        // We can pick `a_0, ..., a_{k_A-1}` as the `k_A` smaller elements.
        // We can pick `a_n, ..., a_{n+k_A-1}` as the `k_A` larger elements.
        // So Class A = `{a_0, ..., a_{k_A-1}, a_{n-1}, a_n, ..., a_{n+k_A-1}}`.
